<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qt3dextras-qabstractcameracontroller.xml">QAbstractCameraController</db:link> sets up and handles input from keyboard, mouse, and other devices. <db:link xlink:href="qt3dextras-qabstractcameracontroller.xml">QAbstractCameraController</db:link> is an abstract class and cannot itself be instantiated. It provides a standard interface for camera controllers.</db:para>
</db:section>
